 Documentary exploring the murder of Meredith Kercher in Italy four years ago, 
 a crime for which American Amanda Knox and her ex-boyfriend Raffaele Sollecito
 were recently acquitted, while a third person, Rudy Guede, remains behind     
 bars. The programme reviews the evidence that convicted Knox and Sollecito,

 system and for Meredith's family.
